@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@token =

### ================== ITINERARY STOP SCHEDULE ==================

### Obtener todos los horarios de paradas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/itinerary-stop-schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear un horario para una parada
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/itinerary-stop-schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itineraryId": 1,
  "stopId": 1,
  "scheduledTime": "07:15:00",
  "status": "ACTIVO"
}

###

### Obtener horario por itinerario y parada
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/itinerary-stop-schedules/1/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar horario por itinerario y parada
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/itinerary-stop-schedules/1/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduledTime": "07:20:00",
  "status": "ACTIVO"
}

###

### Eliminar físicamente un horario
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/itinerary-stop-schedules/1/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Eliminar lógicamente un horario
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/itinerary-stop-schedules/1/1/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
